<br></span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;
<br></span>
<br>&lt;/body&gt;
<br>&lt;/html&gt;</span>
</div><br><a target="_blank" href="http://www.runoob.com/try/runcode.php?filename=demo_intro&type=php" class="showbtn">运行实例 »</a></div>

<p><b>点击"运行实例"按钮查看在线实例运行结果。</b></p>
